Package: shinyfilters
Title: Create 'shiny' Inputs from Vectors, 'data.frames', or any R Object
Version: 0.2.0.9000
Authors@R: c(
    person("Josh", "Livingston", email = "joshwlivingston@gmail.com", role = c("cre", "aut")))
Description: Provides an interface to 'shiny' inputs used for filtering vectors,
  data.frames, and other objects. 'S7'-based implementation allows for seamless 
  extensibility.
